query:
SELECT ea.email, ea.telegram_id, ea.role::text as "role!", ea.status::text as "status!",
                   u.telegram_username
            FROM event_attendees ea
            LEFT JOIN users u ON ea.telegram_id = u.telegram_id
            WHERE ea.event_id = $1
            ORDER BY
                CASE ea.role::text
                    WHEN 'ORGANIZER' THEN 0
                    ELSE 1
                END,
                ea.created_at ASC
